<TopicLayout title="Artificial Intelligence" description="Explore what AI is, how it works, the different types of AI, and its real-world applications across industries." section="ai-data">
  <h2>What is Artificial Intelligence?</h2>
  <p><strong>Artificial Intelligence (AI)</strong> is the simulation of human intelligence processes by machines, especially computer systems. AI enables machines to perform tasks that typically require human intelligence — such as understanding language, recognizing images, making decisions, and learning from experience.</p>

  <h2>Types of AI</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Narrow AI (Weak AI)</strong> — Designed for a specific task. All current AI is narrow AI. Examples: Siri, recommendation engines, face recognition.</li>
    <li><strong>General AI (Strong AI)</strong> — Hypothetical AI that can perform any intellectual task a human can. Does not exist yet.</li>
    <li><strong>Superintelligent AI</strong> — AI that surpasses human intelligence in all areas. Purely theoretical.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Key AI Approaches</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Machine Learning (ML)</strong> — AI learns from data without explicit programming. See <a href="/ai-data/machine-learning">Machine Learning</a>.</li>
    <li><strong>Deep Learning</strong> — A subset of ML using neural networks with many layers. Powers image recognition, language models, and more.</li>
    <li><strong>Natural Language Processing (NLP)</strong> — Enables machines to understand and generate human language. Used in chatbots, translation, and sentiment analysis.</li>
    <li><strong>Computer Vision</strong> — Enables machines to interpret and understand visual information. Used in self-driving cars, medical imaging, and facial recognition.</li>
    <li><strong>Reinforcement Learning</strong> — AI learns by trial and error, receiving rewards for correct actions. Used in game-playing AI (Chess, Go) and robotics.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Real-World AI Applications</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>🏥 <strong>Healthcare</strong> — Disease diagnosis, drug discovery, medical imaging.</li>
    <li>🚗 <strong>Transportation</strong> — Self-driving cars, route optimization, traffic management.</li>
    <li>💬 <strong>Customer Service</strong> — Chatbots, virtual assistants (ChatGPT, Gemini).</li>
    <li>🛒 <strong>E-Commerce</strong> — Product recommendations, fraud detection.</li>
    <li>🎮 <strong>Gaming</strong> — Intelligent NPCs, procedural content generation.</li>
    <li>🔒 <strong>Cybersecurity</strong> — Anomaly detection, threat analysis.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>What's Next?</h2>
